OL,7,FSadiq Khan has signaled the end of the
OL,8,Froad for London's "Boris Bus" in a new
OL,9,Fmission to clean-up the capital's air.
OL,11,FThe bespoke red double deckers ordered
OL,12,Fby previous mayor Boris Johnson at a
OL,13,Fcost of more than #350m have been in
OL,14,Fservice less than 15 years.
OL,16,FBut Khan, re-elected last week for a
OL,17,Fhistoric third term, has pledged to
OL,18,Fmake London's bus-fleet 'zero
OL,19,Femission' by 2030.
