OL,5,Cair
OL,7,FThe aim is to have London's 8,600
OL,8,Fbuses powered by batteries or hydrogen.
OL,10,F"By 2030, all the buses in London will
OL,11,Fbe zero emission," Sadiq Khan said.
OL,13,F"Some may need to be retro-fitted but
OL,14,FI think all will be new buses by 2030.
OL,16,F"It means any bus that is not zero
OL,17,Femission will be off our streets by
OL,18,F2030," he explained.
