OL,7,FThe "Boris Bus" - officially the New
OL,8,FBus For London, or NB4L - was
OL,9,Fcommissioned by Johnson as a
OL,10,Freplacement for the iconic Routemaster.
OL,12,FIt was designed by award-winning
OL,13,FThomas Heatherwick who was also
OL,14,Fresponsible for the London 2012
OL,15,FOlympic cauldron.
OL,17,FThe first batch of a 1,000 new buses
OL,18,Farrived in London from a Northern
OL,19,FIreland factory in 2012.
