OL,7,FThe original Routemaster double
OL,8,Fdecker, with its open platform and
OL,9,Fconductor, was introduced by London
OL,10,FTransport in 1954.
OL,12,FBut the buses were retired in 2005
OL,13,Fafter more than 50 years when London's
OL,14,Ffirst mayor, Ken Livingstone, ordered
OL,15,Fa fleet of bendy buses.
